Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_rx::_stats_octs_dmac

Notes:

  • Cleared either by a write (of any value) or a read when AGL_GMX_RX_STATS_CTL[RD_CLR] is set
  • Counters will wrap
  • Not reset when MIX*_CTL[RESET] is set to 1.
